WEBVTT

00:03.805 --> 00:06.774
We're supposed to be
at a rock concert,

00:06.776 --> 00:08.375
but all I see is <i>rock.</i>

00:08.377 --> 00:09.643
[ Yawns ]

00:09.645 --> 00:10.644
Relax, Miko.

00:10.646 --> 00:12.880
The show doesn't start
for two hours.

00:12.882 --> 00:16.082
Do you know how long I've waited
to see slash monkey?

00:16.085 --> 00:17.151
Uh...
forever!

00:17.153 --> 00:18.986
And it's their only
U.S. date.

00:18.988 --> 00:20.254
There's a shock.

00:20.256 --> 00:22.990
I mean, who doesn't love
obscure Bulgarian shriek metal?

00:22.992 --> 00:24.959
[ Metallic footsteps
and device beeping ]

00:24.961 --> 00:27.628
By all appearances,
the mine's been stripped.

00:27.630 --> 00:29.563
But I'm getting a signal.

00:29.565 --> 00:32.732
It's faint,
but it's definitely Energon.

00:32.735 --> 00:34.201
Whoa!

00:36.004 --> 00:37.137
Doesn't make sense.

00:37.139 --> 00:39.073
This operation
has been abandoned

00:39.075 --> 00:40.374
four, maybe five years.

00:40.376 --> 00:42.810
And Decepticons never leave
Energon behind.

00:42.812 --> 00:44.311
Jack: Uh, guys?

00:47.415 --> 00:49.416
Cool!

00:49.418 --> 00:51.719
She went in.
Unbelievable.

00:51.721 --> 00:53.354
Really?

00:53.356 --> 00:55.055
Have you... met her?

00:55.057 --> 00:56.290
[ Groans ]

00:56.292 --> 00:57.958
Miko, get back here!

00:57.960 --> 01:00.494
It <i>would</i> be kind of
interesting to see.

01:00.496 --> 01:02.529
You know, if it were...
Safe?

01:02.531 --> 01:05.699
A stripped mine can be
structurally unstable, Jack.

01:05.701 --> 01:07.334
I promise to step lightly.

01:08.603 --> 01:11.772
Just don't tell your mom.

01:17.044 --> 01:18.664
♪

01:20.000 --> 01:26.074
